metadata.dc:description: We have described a coronary ischemic syndrome not infrequent. It has been diagnosed only a few times in our medium and it can cause grave risks for the patient if it is not recognized in time and managed in an adequate manner.
metadata.dc:title: Angina de Prinzmetal.
[Prinzmetal's angina].
metadata.dc:publisher: Archivos del Instituto de Cardiologia de Mexico
